'''HTC Incredible S '''(S710E) 是一款由台湾 [[HTC|HTC Corporation]] 公司推出的Android智能手机，中文昵称为“惊艳S”，它搭载了[[Android|Android]] 2.2 Froyo 操作系统，并于2011年2月15日上市。
<ref name=HTCPressRelease>{{cite web|url=http://www.htc.com/us/press/htc-launches-three-new-smartphones-with-htc-sensetrade/29|accessdate=2011-04-13|title=HTC LAUNCHES THREE NEW SMARTPHONES WITH HTC SENSE™|publisher=[[HTC|HTC]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809222737/http://www.htc.com/us/press/htc-launches-three-new-smartphones-with-htc-sensetrade/29|archivedate=2011-08-09}}</ref> 

在2011年的[[全球移動通訊大會|全球移動通訊大會]]（MWC 2011）上，HTC公司展出了它们旗下的[[HTC_Desire_S|HTC Desire S]]和[[HTC_Wildfire_S|HTC Wildfire S]]两台手机，并且宣布HTC Incredible S于2011年2月26日在英国首发，<ref name=exclusiveCWBB>{{cite web|url=http://pressoffice.carphonewarehouse.com/news/item/the_incredible_s_the_incredible_sarah_harding/?phpMyAdmin=AHBslJMinbQ440hrdN48U9K1ZO9|accessdate=2011-04-13|title=THE INCREDIBLE S… THE INCREDIBLE SARAH HARDING|publisher=[[Carphone_Warehouse|Carphone Warehouse]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110825022315/http://pressoffice.carphonewarehouse.com/news/item/the_incredible_s_the_incredible_sarah_harding/?phpMyAdmin=AHBslJMinbQ440hrdN48U9K1ZO9|archive-date=2011-08-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>由[[Girls_Aloud|Girls Aloud]]的[[Sarah_Harding|Sarah Harding]]经销。<ref name=exclusiveCWBB />

HTC Incredible S 是 [[Droid_Incredible|Droid Incredible]]的升级版。

== 历史 ==
=== 开发 ===
在早前, 媒体便透露HTC的新机，代号为 '''''Vivo''''' . 它支持[[CDMA|CDMA]]2000的3G网络，并且将会于2011年5月由运营商[[Verizon|Verizon]]在美国发布。<ref name=incredible2April>{{cite web|url=http://reviews.cnet.com/8301-19736_7-20048872-251.html?tag=mncol;txt|accessdate=2011-04-13|title=Verizon's spring plans confirm Android details|publisher=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-date=2013-01-19|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130119121826/http://reviews.cnet.com/8301-19736_7-20048872-251.html?tag=mncol;txt|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 由于它是 [[Droid_Incredible|Droid Incredible]]的升级版，因此也被称为''Droid Incredible 2'',<ref name=incredible2>{{cite web|url=http://reviews.cnet.com/8301-19736_7-20052850-251.html|accessdate=2011-04-13|title=Final Droid Incredible 2 details coming into focus|publisher=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110413072845/http://reviews.cnet.com/8301-19736_7-20052850-251.html|archive-date=2011-04-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 而且它也是一款全球手机，可以支持 GSM 和 CDMA 两种网络。<ref name=incredible2 />

== 硬件 ==
[[File:HTC_Incredible_S_-_back.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:HTC_Incredible_S_(red)_-_back.png|thumb]]
HTC Incredible S 是一款面向高端的智能手机，它拥有一颗 1GHz [[Snapdragon|Snapdragon]] 高通处理器。在其他硬件方面，它相当于HTC的另一台手机[[Desire_HD|Desire HD]]的升级版。<ref name=DHDSpecs>{{cite web|url=http://www.htc.com/www/product/desirehd/specification.html|accessdate=2011-04-13|title=HTC Desire HD Specifications|publisher=[[HTC|HTC]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110523022339/http://www.htc.com/www/product/desirehd/specification.html|archivedate=2011-05-23}}</ref><ref name=DHDSpecs />


在手机后盖方面延续了HTC Incredible的梯田设计，拥有一种立体感。同时磨砂的外壳设计，既能有更好的手感和防滑作用，也不容易髒。采用800万像素的鏡頭，搭配了两个LED闪光灯。外放扬声器明显的安排在了机身上部靠近闪光灯的位置。<ref name=autoRotate>{{cite web|url=http://www.engadget.com/2011/02/18/htc-incredible-s-auto-rotating-buttons-explained-video/|accessdate=2011-04-13|title=HTC Incredible S auto-rotating buttons explained?|publisher=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|archive-date=2011-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110423023018/http://www.engadget.com/2011/02/18/htc-incredible-s-auto-rotating-buttons-explained-video/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

机身的物理按键不多，僅有音量调节键與电源键。电源键和耳机插口都採用傳統設計放置在頂端，micro USB接口的采用也是趋向国际化的做法。螢幕為800x480分辨率的SLCD型，在功能按键方面采用了觸控功能按键设计，分别有：主页、菜单、返回和搜索四个按键，很到位的是，功能按键会随着屏幕的方向转变而转变。通話部分支援雙SIM卡。

=== 版本差异 ===
HTC Incredible S拥有不同版本。加拿大版本在屏幕四周都有铬金属，欧洲版本和亚太版本部分机型则没有双通道的通话孔、摄像头透镜片、LED闪光灯和立体声扬声器。<ref name=chromeAccents>{{cite web|url=http://www.howardforums.com/content.php/488-HTC-Incredible-S-Review|accessdate=2011-04-13|title=HTC Incredible S Review|publisher=[[HowardForums|HowardForums]]|archive-date=2011-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110410214023/http://www.howardforums.com/content.php/488-HTC-Incredible-S-Review|dead-url=no}}</ref>一个针对香港和新加坡的红色版本也已在产。<ref name=redIS>{{cite web|url=http://www.smartone-vodafone.com/jsp/phone/english/detail_v3.jsp?id=1534|accessdate=2011-05-05|title=HTC Incredible S Phone Details|publisher=[[SmarTone_Mobile_Communications_Limited|SmarTone Mobile Communications Limited]]|archive-date=2011-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721022352/http://www.smartone-vodafone.com/jsp/phone/english/detail_v3.jsp?id=1534|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 软件 ==
HTC于2011年第二季度为Incredible S升级到[[Android歷史版本#Android_2.3.x|Android 2.3]]。<ref name=GBUpgrade>{{cite web|url=http://news.softpedia.com/news/HTC-Android-2-3-for-Desire-Desire-HD-Desire-Z-Incredible-S-in-Spring-186457.shtml|accessdate=2011-04-13|title=HTC: Android 2.3 for Desire, Desire HD, Desire Z, Incredible S in Spring|publisher=[[Softpedia|Softpedia]]|archive-date=2011-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110301121822/http://news.softpedia.com/news/HTC-Android-2-3-for-Desire-Desire-HD-Desire-Z-Incredible-S-in-Spring-186457.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年第二季度更升级至[[Android歷史版本#Android_4.0.x|Android 4.0]]。<ref name=ICSUpgrade>{{cite web|url=http://www.htc.com/www/help/android4faq/|accessdate=2012-10-11|title=Android 4.0 Update Frequently Asked Questions- HTC Support Center|publisher=[[宏達國際電子|宏達國際電子]]|archive-date=2012-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007090019/http://www.htc.com/www/help/android4faq/|dead-url=no}}</ref>该机拥有第二代[[HTC_Sense|HTC Sense]]用户界面，后更升级至第三代，内置了全新的[[卫星导航系统|全球卫星导航]]（30天试用），登錄認證碼後則可在該國家永久免費使用。在英国发布的时候，英国的地图也已经包含到了8GB [[microSD|microSD]]卡内。该机拥有[[啟動程式|Bootloader]]，是HTC全新一代智能手机之一。正因如此，该机獲得[[root_(Android)|Root]]權限的門檻也較高<ref name=LockedBootloader>{{cite web|url=http://blog.gsmarena.com/htc-incredible-s-has-a-signed-bootloader-and-recovery-will-htc-phones-become-less-custom-rom-friendly/|accessdate=2011-05-24|title=HTC Incredible S has a signed bootloader and recovery, will HTC phones become less custom ROM friendly?|publisher=[[gsmarena|gsmarena]]|archive-date=2011-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110701230412/http://blog.gsmarena.com/htc-incredible-s-has-a-signed-bootloader-and-recovery-will-htc-phones-become-less-custom-rom-friendly/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。


